data.description: Welcome to 1122 Canyon Brook in the beautiful Canyon Creek Bluff community! This wonderful home awaits its new owners!  Property features include: brick & stucco exterior, mature trees, leveled lot, manicured lawn with great curb appeal, 2 stories, 4 bedrooms, 2.5 bathrooms, 2 eating areas, high ceilings in the living area, fireplace, ceramic tile/engineered wood/carpet flooring, ceiling fans & chandelier lighting, updated kitchen, built-in oven & microwave, granite countertops, center island, stainless steel appliances, glass-front cabinets, natural lighting throughout, owners retreat downstairs with dual sinks, dual countertops, garden tub, walk-in shower, walk-in closet, rear exterior deck overlooks spacious backyard, beautifully surrounded by a wood privacy fence!  Scroll the pictures then schedule your walk-through tour!
